-- Latvian Parliament Approves EU’s Fiscal Stability Treaty
-- B y   A a r o n   E g l i t i s
-- 2012-05-31T09:40:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-31/latvian-parliament-approves-eu-s-fiscal-stability-treaty.html
Latvia’s parliament approved the
European Union’s Fiscal Stability Treaty.  The 100-member legislature voted 67-29 with one abstention
to approve the pact in a second and final reading today,
according to the website of the parliament in the capital, Riga.
The accord anchors balanced-budget rules in national law.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aaron Eglitis in Riga at 
 aeglitis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
